Compilation flags:
========================================
Enable : MODEL=HYDRO, GRAVITY, GREP, EOS=EOS_NUCLEAR
Disable:

Default setup:
========================================
1. Enable external potential
   --> OPT__EXT_POT = 3

Note:
========================================
1. A test problem for core-collapse supernova simulations
   --> initial condition is generated from FLASH, 15 ms after core bounce

      data_s20GREP_SFHo_15ms           : SFHo  nuclear EoS
      data_s20GREP_LS220_nonupres_15ms : LS220 nuclear EoS

